Kabwata bụ mpaghara nke National Assembly nke Zambia
Ọ gụnyere mpaghara Lusaka nke Kabwata, Libala na Chilenje na Lusaka District nke Lusaka Province.

N'ọnwa Septemba nke afọ 2001, e mere ntuli aka elu mgbe a chụpụrụ onye omeiwu nọ n'ọkwa Godfrey Miyanda na Movement for Multi-Party Democracy (MMD) na ndị minista itoolu. MMD (onye gosipụtara Dominic Laban Nyirongo), United National Independence Party (onye gosiputara Kamoyo Mwale) na Forum for Democracy and Development (onye gosipputara Richard Kachingwe) meriri ntuli aka ahụ
Kachingwe meriri na ntuli aka ahụ, ọ bụ ezie na ọ bụ naanị onye omeiwu maka ọnwa ole na ole ka a na-eme ntuli aka n'ozuzu na 27 Disemba 2001.
